#: ../../user_manual/ai-zenith.rst:23
msgid ""
"You can point to the Zenith by pressing **Z** or by selecting the "
"``Pointing`` → ``Zenith`` menu item."
msgstr ""
"Podeu apuntar cap al zenit prement la tecla **Z** o seleccionant l'element "
"de menú ``Apunta`` → ``Zenit``."
